<P>
   FOR MONDAY AMs
</P>
<P>
   Business Day Front Page (coded ``f'' unless otherwise noted): &QL;
</P>
<P>
   (Lede story)
</P>
<P>
   BRILL-MEDIA (Undated) _ While media critics, talk-show hosts and
reporters rehashed the scoop in the first issue of Brill's Content
about Kenneth Starr's leaks in the Monica Lewinsky case, an
entirely different group tipped their hats and took notes: magazine
publicists. By Robin Pogrebin.
</P>
<P>
