u e &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-ELIMINATE-FREUD-EXHIB     07-05 0033
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-ELIMINATE-FREUD-EXHIBIT-NYT </SLUG>
  
<TEXT>
<P>
   EDITORS:
</P>
<P>
   FREUD-EXHIBIT (Undated) will not move in tonight's New York
Times News Service file.
</P>
<P>
   N.Y.Times News Service, July 5.
</P>
</TEXT>
