1977, 1978 and 1996.
</P>
<ANNOTATION>
   (STORY CAN END HERE. OPTIONAL MATERIAL FOLLOWS)
</ANNOTATION>
<P>
   ``Sesame Street'' producers might consider using the Yankees as
