<HEADLINE>
BOSTON GLOBE QUESTIONS 48 ADDITIONAL COLUMNS 
</HEADLINE>
  (Duplication warning: Also moving in `f' category) 
(pr) 
 By FELICITY BARRINGER   
 c.1998 N.Y. Times News Service   
